cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper deals with 3D object detection in autonomous vehicles using multiple sensors, including cameras and LiDAR. This falls under the categories of computer vision (cs.CV), robotics (cs.RO), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the use of siamese networks for re-identification and association of objects relates to multimedia (cs.MM).
